1249
01:10:14,265 --> 01:10:16,082
battle over the deputy foreman.

1250
01:10:16,082 --> 01:10:20,185
But the Virginian seemed to find nothing
save enjoyment in this sunny September

1251
01:10:20,185 --> 01:10:23,390
morning, and ate his
breakfast at Forsythe serenely.

1252
01:10:23,390 --> 01:10:28,145
That meal done and that station gone,
