01:16:48,237 --> 01:16:50,097
“Yes, woman.

1393
01:16:50,097 --> 01:16:55,121
Didn’t I tell yu’ the botanist
had his wife along?

1394
01:16:55,121 --> 01:16:56,688
Well, he did.

