enough to amputate my thumb,
and none of us chewed,

1398
01:17:07,085 --> 01:17:11,770
and the doctor was twenty miles away,
and if he had only remembered to bring

1399
01:17:11,770 --> 01:17:16,771
his ammonia⁠—well, he was screeching out
’most everything he knew in the world,

1400
01:17:16,771 --> 01:17:19,742
and without arranging it any, neither.

1401
01:17:19,742 --> 01:17:22,733
But she just clawed his pocket and
burrowed and kep’ yelling,

1402
01:17:22,733 --> 01:17:24,425
‘Give him the stone, Augustus!’

1403
01:17:24,425 --> 01:17:28,521
And she whipped out one of them Injun
