01:39:22,493 --> 01:39:23,652
“Not exactly!”

1871
01:39:23,652 --> 01:39:25,214
the traveller exclaimed.

1872
01:39:25,214 --> 01:39:28,126
“How much would be paid for frogs?”

1873
01:39:28,126 --> 01:39:29,741
said Trampas to him.

1874
01:39:29,741 --> 01:39:33,844
