1882
01:39:56,558 --> 01:40:00,663
He allowed himself a broad
smile of retrospect.

1883
01:40:00,663 --> 01:40:02,683
“To hear ’em talk frawgs at Tulare!

1884
01:40:02,683 --> 01:40:06,333
Same as other folks talks hawsses or
steers or whatever they’re

1885
01:40:06,333 --> 01:40:07,417
raising to sell.

1886
01:40:07,417 --> 01:40:11,425
Yu’d fall into it yourselves if
yu’ started the business.

1887
01:40:11,425 --> 01:40:15,116
Anything a man’s bread and butter depends
on, he’s going to be earnest about.

1888
01:40:15,116 --> 01:40:17,160
