restaurants in San Francisco, yu’ see.

1912
01:41:32,737 --> 01:41:34,508
And there was the Cliff House.

1913
01:41:34,508 --> 01:41:37,778
And the Palace Hotel made it a specialty.

1914
01:41:37,778 --> 01:41:41,501
And the officers took frawgs at the
Presidio, an’ Angel Island,

1915
01:41:41,501 --> 01:41:43,969
an’ Alcatraz, an’ Benicia.

1916
01:41:43,969 --> 01:41:47,510
Los Angeles was beginnin’ its boom.

1917
01:41:47,510 --> 01:41:51,592
The corner-lot sharps wanted something
by way of varnish.

1918
01:41:51,592 --> 01:41:58,490
An’ so they dazzled Eastern investors
with advertisin’ Tulare frawgs clear to

1919
01:41:58,490 --> 01:42:00,880
New Orleans an’ New York.

1920
01:42:00,880 --> 01:42:05,466
’Twas only in Sacramento frawgs was dull.

1921
01:42:05,466 --> 01:42:09,385
I expaict the California legislature was
too or’n’ry for them

1922
01:42:09,385 --> 01:42:11,210
fine-raised luxuries.

1923
01:42:11,210 --> 01:42:16,067
They tell of one of them senators that he
raked a million out of Los Angeles real

1924
01:42:16,067 --> 01:42:19,747
estate, and started in for a bang-
up meal with champagne.

1925
01:42:19,747 --> 01:42:23,202
Wanted to scatter his new
gold thick an’ quick.

1926
01:42:23,202 --> 01:42:28,017
