dishes, an’ just yelled right out before

1927
01:42:28,017 --> 01:42:29,645
the ladies, ‘Damn it!

1928
01:42:29,645 --> 01:42:32,364
bring me forty dollars’ worth
of ham and aiggs.’

1929
01:42:32,364 --> 01:42:33,861
He was a funny senator, now.”

1930
01:42:33,861 --> 01:42:36,586
The Virginian paused,
