2007
01:46:34,727 --> 01:46:38,887
drugged by their satanically aroused
hopes of gold, heedless of the

2008
01:46:38,887 --> 01:46:40,949
slippers and the spurs.

2009
01:46:40,949 --> 01:46:45,160
Had a man given any sign to warn them,
