01:46:57,592 --> 01:47:00,068
And they watched him with approval.

2014
01:47:00,068 --> 01:47:04,594
He sat by the fire with the frying-pan,
looking his daily self⁠—

2015
01:47:04,594 --> 01:47:06,915
engaging and saturnine.

2016
01:47:06,915 --> 01:47:13,199
And now as Trampas declared tickets to
