2019
01:47:22,285 --> 01:47:24,431
“I said it was too late for Tulare.”

2020
01:47:24,431 --> 01:47:26,882
“I heard you,” said Trampas.

2021
01:47:26,882 --> 01:47:28,402
“Opinions may differ.

2022
01:47:28,402 --> 01:47:31,148
You and I don’t think
alike on several points.”

2023
01:47:31,148 --> 01:47:32,981
“Gawd, Trampas!”

2024
01:47:32,981 --> 01:47:37,695
said the Virginian, “d’ yu’ reckon I’d be
