2032
01:47:55,810 --> 01:47:58,494
again to hear a tale of blood.

2033
01:47:58,494 --> 01:48:00,543
The crowd seemed to lean nearer.

2034
01:48:00,543 --> 01:48:04,703
But for a short moment it
threatened to be spoiled.

2035
01:48:04,703 --> 01:48:08,758
A passenger came along,
demanding in an important voice,

2036
01:48:08,758 --> 01:48:10,379
“Where are these frogs?”

2037
01:48:10,379 --> 01:48:14,906
He was a prominent New York after-dinner
speaker, they whispered me,

2038
01:48:14,906 --> 01:48:17,925
and out for a holiday in his private
car.

2039
01:48:17,925 --> 01:48:23,400
