01:49:37,344 --> 01:49:42,464
“Aimed to cut away the trade from Saynt
Augustine an’ put Philadelphia back

2068
01:49:42,464 --> 01:49:44,090
where he thought she belonged.

2069
01:49:44,090 --> 01:49:46,763
Frawgs was the fashionable rage then.

2070
01:49:46,763 --> 01:49:49,764
These foreign cooks set the fashion in
