either o’ those positions.

2434
02:11:19,427 --> -1:59:59,000
How many religions are there?

2435
-1:59:59,000 --> 00:00:02,000
”

2436
02:11:21,409 --> 02:11:22,462
“All over the earth?”

2437
02:11:22,462 --> 02:11:24,626
“Yu’ can begin with ourselves.

2438
02:11:24,626 --> 02:11:28,594
