2555
02:17:48,740 --> -1:59:59,000
Or maybe yu’ expected me to notice
and⁠—not take notice?

2556
-1:59:59,000 --> 00:00:02,000
”

2557
02:17:53,185 --> 02:17:56,597
“I don’t spend my time
in expectations about you.

2558
02:17:56,597 --> 02:17:57,214
If⁠—”

2559
02:17:57,214 --> 02:18:00,476
The Virginian wheeled his
horse across the road.

2560
02:18:00,476 --> 02:18:05,081
“Yu’re talkin’ too soon
after reachin’ safety, Trampas.

2561
02:18:05,081 --> 02:18:09,925
I didn’t tell yu’ to hand me that rope
