2562
02:18:09,925 --> 02:18:11,274
I ain’t foreman now;

2563
02:18:11,274 --> 02:18:13,298
and I want that rope.”

2564
02:18:13,298 --> 02:18:17,570
Trampas produced a smile as
skilful as his voice.

2565
02:18:17,570 --> 02:18:21,780
“Well, I guess your having mine proves
this one is yours.”

2566
02:18:21,780 --> 02:18:25,518
He rode up and received the coil which
the Virginian held out,

2567
02:18:25,518 --> 02:18:27,994
unloosing the disputed one on his
saddle.

2568
02:18:27,994 --> 02:18:33,218
If he had meant to devise a slippery,
evasive insult, no small trick in cow-

2569
02:18:33,218 --> 02:18:37,811
land could be more offensive than this
taking another man’s rope.

2570
02:18:37,811 --> 02:18:43,567
And it is the small tricks which lead
to the big bullets.

2571
02:18:43,567 --> 02:18:49,117
Trampas put a smooth coating of
plausibility over the whole transaction.

2572
02:18:49,117 --> 02:18:52,916
“After the rope corral we had to make
