2610
02:21:06,350 --> 02:21:10,732
It was another evasive little business,
and quite successful,

2611
02:21:10,732 --> 02:21:13,332
if designed to nag the owner of the
rope.

2612
02:21:13,332 --> 02:21:19,748
A few hundred yards ahead of us Trampas
