2613
02:21:19,748 --> 02:21:24,222
Were they to announce his return to those
at home, or did they mean derision?

2614
02:21:24,222 --> 02:21:27,643
The Virginian leaned,
keeping his seat, and,

2615
02:21:27,643 --> 02:21:31,397
swinging down his arm,
caught up the rope, and hung it on

2616
02:21:31,397 --> 02:21:33,339
his saddle somewhat carefully.

2617
02:21:33,339 --> 02:21:37,571
But the hue of rage spread over his face.

2618
02:21:37,571 --> 02:21:41,531
From his fence the divine now spoke,
in approbation, but with

2619
02:21:41,531 --> 02:21:43,892
another strong, cheerless smile.

2620
02:21:43,892 --> 02:21:47,223
“You pick up that rope as if you were
well trained to it.”

2621
02:21:47,223 --> 02:21:50,373
“It’s part of our business,
seh, and we try to mind

2622
02:21:50,373 --> 02:21:51,683
it like the rest.”

2623
02:21:51,683 --> 02:21:57,072
But this, stated in a gentle drawl,
did not pierce the missionary’s armor;

2624
02:21:57,072 --> 02:22:00,147
his superiority was very thick.

2625
02:22:00,147 --> 02:22:05,708
We now rode on, and I was impressed by
the reverend gentleman’s robust,

2626
02:22:05,708 --> 02:22:09,873
dictatorial back as he proceeded by a
shortcut through the meadow to the

2627
02:22:09,873 --> 02:22:10,613
ranch.

2628
02:22:10,613 --> 02:22:14,979
You could take him for nothing but a
vigorous, sincere, dominating man,

2629
02:22:14,979 --> 02:22:17,425
full of the highest purpose.

2630
02:22:17,425 --> 02:22:20,464
But whatever his creed,
I already doubted if he were the right

2631
02:22:20,464 --> 02:22:25,121
one to sow it and make it grow in
these new, wild fields.

2632
02:22:25,121 --> 02:22:28,496
He seemed more the sort of gardener to
keep old walks and vines pruned

2633
02:22:28,496 --> 02:22:30,256
in their antique rigidity.

2634
02:22:30,256 --> 02:22:34,854
I admired him for coming all this way
with his clean, short,

2635
02:22:34,854 --> 02:22:38,972
gray whiskers and his
black, well-brushed suit.

2636
02:22:38,972 --> 02:22:42,938
And he made me think of a powerful
locomotive stuck puffing on a grade.

2637
02:22:42,938 --> 02:22:48,727
Meanwhile, the Virginian rode beside me,
so silent in his volcanic wrath that I

2638
02:22:48,727 --> 02:22:49,929
did not perceive it.

2639
02:22:49,929 --> 02:22:54,221
The missionary coming on top of Trampas
