2661
02:23:55,674 --> 02:23:58,615
This was his full apology.

2662
02:23:58,615 --> 02:24:04,486
“As for salvation, I have got this far:
somebody,” he swept an arm at the sunset

2663
02:24:04,486 --> 02:24:07,800
and the mountains, “must have made
