2664
02:24:07,800 --> 02:24:12,847
But I know one more thing I would tell
Him to His face: if I can’t do nothing

2665
02:24:12,847 --> 02:24:17,467
long enough and good enough to earn
eternal happiness, I can’t do nothing

2666
02:24:17,467 --> 02:24:20,746
long enough and bad enough to be damned.

2667
02:24:20,746 --> 02:24:25,517
I reckon He plays a square game with us
if He plays at all, and I ain’t

2668
02:24:25,517 --> -1:59:59,000
bothering my haid about other worlds.

2669
-1:59:59,000 --> 00:00:02,000
”

2670
02:24:28,045 --> 02:24:31,576
As we reached the stables,
