02:25:50,095 --> 02:25:53,083
The Virginian was brief about this fact.

2696
02:25:53,083 --> 02:25:54,659
“I’ll look afteh your saddle.

2697
02:25:54,659 --> 02:25:56,915
You go and get acquainted
with the company.”

