02:27:33,744 --> 02:27:38,304
MacBride had fixed upon me his full,
mastering eye; and it occurred to me

2726
02:27:38,304 --> 02:27:42,144
that if they had policemen in heaven,
he would be at least a

2727
02:27:42,144 --> 02:27:43,424
centurion in the force.

2728
02:27:43,424 --> 02:27:47,864
But he did not mean to be unpleasant;
