2735
02:28:08,398 --> 02:28:12,000
“Yes,” said Judge Henry, “yes.

2736
02:28:12,000 --> 02:28:13,167
It would be a good thing.”

2737
02:28:13,167 --> 02:28:13,560
Mrs.

